hague convention for the protection of c.data-term: hague convention for the protection of cultural property in the event of armed conflict

examples.en: This writer plundered from famous authors.
examples.ru: Этот писатель занимался плагиатом у известных авторов.

examples.en: Thieves had long ago plundered the tomb.
The village was plundered by the invading army.
The rich provinces of Asia Minor were plundered by the invaders.
examples.ru: Богатые провинции Малой Азии были разграблены оккупантами.

examples.en: All evidence suggested that the plunder of the tomb had happened long ago.
examples.ru: Всё свидетельствует о том, что разграбление данной гробницы произошло давным-давно.

examples.en: The soldiers continued plundering for days.
Henry's army returned loaded down with plunder.
